      • type

        public void type(CharSequence characters,
                 boolean isHuman)
        Sends messages that replicate the function of the keyboard and uses this to type the input.
        Parameters:
        characters - The input to type
        isHuman - If true, adds a random Thread.Sleep() before and after every key down event, including shift if a special character needs it or if the character in question is upper case.
